{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to know what's in the lift van, and did we smuggle some gold out and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came from what was called [SPEAKING GERMAN], the agency concerned with smuggling and goods crossing the border and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very fortunately, my mother was not at home, because she was not up to these things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was young and strong and healthy and gutsy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, I went with them to the office of the [SPEAKING GERMAN], but they were very busy there, so they put me down in the waiting room.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by then it got late and the-- the official there had no time for an interview, whatever they intended to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they put me in a broom closet in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there I was in the broom closet, locked in, and I was just standing there and wondering, what next?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you saw the lights through the crack in the door and heard the-- the footsteps and nothing else to do but to listen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can't plan.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's nothing to plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's this-- I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so my amusement was that these footsteps were the footsteps of these SS people and the footsteps of the secretaries, clip, clop with their high heels-- kind of a musical entertainment, very funny.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the lights dimmed, and the [IMITATING FOOTSTEPS] left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the clip clop ended.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was locked in the broom closet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I started to holler and to scream, and somebody came, unlocked the broom closet, and was extremely surprised to find a person among the brooms and didn't know what to do with that person.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By then, it was maybe 6:00.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
